HEADWORD: Livre
<hw>Li"vre</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[F., fr. L.
<ets>libra</ets> a pound of twelve ounces. Cf. <er>Lira</er>.]</ety>
<def>A French money of account, afterward a silver coin equal to 20
sous. It is not now in use, having been superseded by the
franc.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

